{'text': "I've always wanted a marine reef tank and when I opened a business in the block next door, I went to them. I don't know if it's appropriate to publicly name them but the lovely couple who are owners of the shop have been beyond amazing at helping me with choices, advice, suggestions, picking the right marine life. They even took the time and effort to teach me about ammonia and nitrates and all of that beginner stuff.
Very good selection of fish. I get my marine water from them (they are right next door.). Thank you so much Ms. J@@@@@@ and Mr S@@!
I am so grateful, and I'm appreciating the fish. One of my life's dream coming true: ocean with me. Thank you.
